%N A167653 Number of reduced words of length n in Coxeter group on 8 generators S_i with relations (S_i)^2 = (S_i S_j)^15 = I.
%C A167653 The initial terms coincide with those of A003950, although the two sequences are eventually different.
%C A167653 Computed with Magma using commands similar to those used to compute A154638.
%H A167653 G. C. Greubel, <a href="/A167653/b167653.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..500</a>
